collections.name: Tokasino
collections.description: "Welcome to the 'Token' collection, a unique and innovative project that blends digital art, history, and blockchain technology in a journey through time. This exclusive series of NFTs, each distinct in design and meaning from month to month, spans from March 2025 to December 2050, offering a surprising and unrepeatable variety. Every Token is crafted as a unique digital artwork with a vintage aesthetic, inspired by the month and year its token, making each piece a singular fragment of a broader narrative.

collections.name: Photograph of Modern Art
collections.description:
"A limited-edition industrial photograph capturing the recursive deconstruction of artistic intent in the post-industrial landscape. This piece serves as a critique of the evolving relationship between meaning, perception, and value, transforming the act of observation into a layered commentary on artistic commodification. The machines are unnecessary, there is "modern art beauty in them" ... THEY are the modern art. THIS is The Photograph of Modern art."

The work has been provided fully by author. The concept was found out by the author. The other nonsense surrounding the process was done in close cooperation of the author with AI. None is full AI here, except price.

The pricing of this collection was not determined by human whim, but by an AI "chat" explicitly designed for logic, non-magical thinking, and contradiction-free reasoning. The AI was prompted with every detail of the process, every decision made, and in the end—this is the price it set. This is the value it determined."

collections.name: Food Ape Society
collections.description:
MINTING NOW. Head to X ( pinned Tweet ) or Discord.
Food Ape Society is an exclusive collectables project designed by the artist TheFoodMaster. TheFoodMaster is the working alias for Corina Daniela Obertas, an Italian-based food photographer, food concept and multidisciplinary artist. 
There are 520 Food Ape Society NFTs minted on the Ethereum blockchain, as ERC-721A.
The collection stands out for its varied representation of global culinary cultures, transforming each NFT into a true ambassador of the world’s unique flavours. 
If you buy a Food Ape Society NFT, you do not receive commercial rights to the corresponding artwork.
